h3 What other information is public?
p Information you post on the Sites, event pages, campaign pages, personal fundraising or pledge pages, your profile (unless hidden), a charity or sponsor profile, blog posts, or other public pages on the Sites can be accessed by other people. You should exercise caution when deciding to share information on public pages. We cannot control who accesses shared information or how other parties will use that information.

// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

h3 What choices do I have?
p It’s up to you whether or not you want to provide us with Personal Information. You can still visit the Sites without providing us with Personal information, but you will be unable to take certain actions without doing so.

